{
  "text": "Is it impossible for you to tell us precisely how he does this service? I am Ra. It is possible for us to speak to this query. However we use any chance we may have to reiterate the basic understanding learning that all beings serve the Creator, the one you speak of as Genghis Khan at present is incarnate in a physical light body which has the work of disseminating material of thought control to those who are what you may call Crusagers. He is, as you would term this entity, a shipping clerk.",
